missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: The Empire was not slow to crack down on Sullust. Their chief political official has been arrested and is now being transported by heavily guarded convoy to Coruscant. This is a great blow to our hope of securing Sullustan support. But swift action now may yet swing Sullustan support for the Alliance. Gold Squadron will jump in and destroy the convoy’s escort. While Y-Wings from Red Squadron jump in to disable the prisoner transport. Before our Rescue shuttle jumps in to liberate their leader.
Red Squadron head to the jump point immediately.
Red Squadron switch to ion cannons and disable those Sentinels. I'll take the Lambda.
Target ship disabled. Activating beacon for boarding craft.
Hostage secured. Commence release from docking.
Another Lancer class frigate is entering the area. Prepare for more fighters!
Thanks for the cover Red Squadron. We'll see you back at the fleet.
Okay Red Squadron. Make a break for the jump point.
This is Dagger One, the target is marked and we're beginning our approach.

missionEventData.data3: With the liberation of their leader, the Sullustan people have thrown their support behind the Rebel Alliance, bringing much needed ships and supplies to our cause. But their greatest gift is something unexpected…

missionEventData.data1: That Lancer Class Frigate is dropping fighters!
We need to destroy those Fighters before we can make the jump to Hyperspace.
Okay Red Squadron move to engage those Ties
